Betting Rules

Rule Requirement Why
Bet Type UNDERS ONLY Model predicts regression, not breakouts
Edge 3+ points Smaller edges dont overcome vig

What NOT To Do

  • Never bet OVERS - They lose 10%+ ROI historically
  • Never bet bad odds - Anything worse than -115 eats your profit
  • Never bet small edges - Under 3 points isnt worth the risk
  • Never bet everything - Be selective, not comprehensive
